title: "You fed him"
body:
Listen mate,
it's minute 50... everyone is full build.
Being fed isn't a factor anymore.

replies.body:
"you fed him"
=
You allowed this champion to get stronger than the rest of us (who all went even) and effectively take over the game resulting in us being pushed in to our base with way less opportunity to press any advantage before late game because we are busy peeling X champion off of our carries.
Some champions are stronger late than early so if you fed a late game hypercarry or you fed bot and gave away botlane dragon pressure.
